6 20 L20 24 L16 28\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"22\" y1=\"28\" x2=\"28\" y2=\"28\"/></svg>      </div>\n      <div class=\"hydra-sp-body\">\n        <h3>Computer System Validation</h3>\n        <div class=\"hydra-sp-chips\">\n          <span class=\"hydra-chip hydra-chip--h1\"><span class=\"hydra-chip-dot\"></span>computer system validation services</span>\n          <span class=\"hydra-chip hydra-chip--h2\"><span class=\"hydra-chip-dot hydra-chip-dot--gray\"></span>GAMP 5 validation</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>GAMP 5, 21 CFR Part 11, EU Annex 11. Only Saudi-based CSV provider.</p>\n        <span class=\"hydra-sp-cta\">View page &rarr;</span>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Card 9: Cold Chain Solutions -->\n    <a href=\"/services/cold-chain-solutions-saudi-arabia/\" class=\"hydra-sp-card hydra-sp-card--dark\">\n      <div class=\"hydra-sp-img\" style=\"background:#0C1E28\">\n        <svg width=\"48\" height=\"48\" viewBox=\"0 0 48 48\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#016B7A\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"4\" y=\"18\" width=\"26\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"/><path d=\"M30 22 L40 22 L44 28 L44 34 L30 34\"/><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"38\" r=\"4\"/><circle cx=\"34\" cy=\"38\" r=\"4\"/><line x1=\"8\" y1=\"26\" x2=\"22\" y2=\"26\"/></svg>      </div>\n      <div class=\"hydra-sp-body\">\n        <h3>Cold Chain Solutions <span class=\"hydra-sp-badge\">New</span></h3>\n        <div class=\"hydra-sp-chips\">\n          <span class=\"hydra-chip hydra-chip--h1\"><span class=\"hydra-chip-dot\"></span>cold chain solutions Saudi Arabia</span>\n          <span class=\"hydra-chip hydra-chip--h2\"><span class=\"hydra-chip-dot hydra-chip-dot--gray\"></span>GDP transport solutions</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>GDP transport compliance, audit readiness and gap assessment — in one place.</p>\n        <span class=\"hydra-sp-cta\">View page &rarr;</span>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n\n    <!-- Card 10: Temperature Data Logger -->